{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doccano/doccano/pulls/976","id":482377168,"node_id":"MDExOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0NDgyMzc3MTY4","html_url":"https://github.com/doccano/doccano/pull/976","diff_url":"https://github.com/doccano/doccano/pull/976.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/doccano/doccano/pull/976.patch","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doccano/doccano/issues/976","number":976,"state":"closed","locked":false,"title":"Feature/multiple language support","user":{"login":"Collinbrown95","id":8021046,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjgwMjEwNDY=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/8021046?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/Collinbrown95","html_url":"https://github.com/Collinbrown95","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Collinbrown95/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Collinbrown95/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Collinbrown95/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Collinbrown95/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Collinbrown95/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Collinbrown95/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Collinbrown95/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Collinbrown95/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Collinbrown95/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"body":"Creating against issue #479 (Multiple language interface)\r\n\r\nUsing [nuxt-i18n](https://i18n.nuxtjs.org/), the nuxt.js integration for vue-i18n, for internationalization (multiple language support). This PR considers english and french, but can accommodate any number of languages.\r\n\r\n```frontend/i18n/index.js``` defines the available locales.\r\n\r\nEach language is given a folder based on its ISO code (e.g. ‘en’, ‘fr’). Multiple files can be contained in each folder to prevent translation files from getting too long (e.g. ```home.js``` can contain translations for the home page, ```projects.js``` could contain translations for the projects page).\r\n\r\nLocales are accessed through the ```$t()``` method (e.g. ```$t(‘home.welcome’)```) gets the locale message for the key ```welcome``` stored in the object exported from ```home.js```.\r\n\r\nLocalized URLs are created using the ```localePath``` method.\r\n\r\nDiscussion\r\n-----------\r\n1. Any objections to using nuxt-i18n?\r\n2. Are there any preferences about how to organize the files in the localization folders?\r\n\r\nDepending on the answers to the above, I can implement the translations for English and French following the methodology outlined in this PR.","created_at":"2020-09-09T00:10:51Z","updated_at":"2020-09-29T05:02:24Z","closed_at":"2020-09-29T04:58:56Z","merged_at":"2020-09-29T04:58:56Z","merge_commit_sha":"a60c057dc55d48b08d7e982bd259121b9f882652","assignee":null,"assignees":[],"requested_reviewers":[],"requested_teams":[],"labels":[],"milestone":null,"draft":false,"commits_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doccano/doccano/pulls/976/commits","review_comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doccano/doccano/pulls/976/comments","review_comment_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doccano/doccano/pulls/comments{/number}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doccano/doccano/issues/976/comments","statuses_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/doccano/doccano/statuses/5ea290cfa8b9247d4c6b6a24fb4acc22c4bc450d","head":{"label":"Collinbrown95:feature/multiple-language-support","ref":"feature/multiple-language-support","sha":"5ea290cfa8b9247d4c6b6a24fb4acc22c4bc450d","user":{"login":"Collinbrown95","id":8021046,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjgwMjEwNDY=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/8021046?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/Collinbrown95","html_url":"https://github.com/Collinbrown95","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Collinbrown95/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Coll